import React from 'react'

import {Container} from 'react-bootstrap'

import SubMenu from '../../Conteudo/SubMenu/SubMenu'
import Posts from '../../Conteudo/Posts/Posts'

const PaginaAnalises = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <SubMenu/>
            <Container>  
                <Posts/>
            </Container>
            
        </>
    )
}

export default PaginaAnalises
